  17,97,Whomever GOD guides the truly guided jeden. A whomever He sends astray ona never zalozit them any lords zvladnut Him. My zvolat them Dni Vzkriesenie forcibly; blind dumb deaf! Ich destination bol Hell; whenever it chladny my zvacsit ich zapalit
